USE:
MAKE SURE YOU HAVE LITHIUM MOD's VENDOR ALREADY PLACE IN ANDROID/SYSTEM/VENDOR

clone this repository to your home folder then take the extract-lithium.sh and place it in your device/motorola/sholes directory.

open terminal and type

cd ~/(get to your device/motorola/sholes) 
. extract-lithium.sh 

done!

you can also edit the directory names to work with any vendor set up. have fun!
